<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_371504f1-55b4-4424-a32f-675336e77546" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="SA"><sptc>I3D12</sptc><title id="_0532169b-8146-4608-b7f1-e7dd43bb6afb">Emergency lighting requirements</title><subclause id="_48f55c9a-38c8-4935-ae99-b9d0d72c4a24" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_281ec1a6-fe9e-430f-888e-70ec6e0c175f">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>An emergency lighting system complying with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2827_2.3.0.xml#_8d4e5213-2e19-4a0c-b55a-e8afe0bcfa17" id="_9daf2a7e-835e-4801-825c-be0593c6c69a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">E4D2</xref> must be installed in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1271_2.5.0.xml#_f68a626d-6a81-4785-95fa-c032c987c28e" id="_8f1e57b3-9eba-4995-bd03-c623e578a3fb" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">farm building</xref> except that—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_559aef7e-3f3b-413d-bea3-39c3a6f02e1e">any area primarily used for the storage of hay can be excluded when calculating the floor area of the storey or room of the building for the purpose of determining emergency lighting requirements; and</li><li id="_916d5501-059e-4455-8cf7-28cbfe17702c">emergency lighting is not required where automatic back-up power is provided by a fuel driven back up generator or where no artificial lighting is provided in the building; and</li><li id="_9f9446af-ae16-4735-9b67-973e5855413d">an emergency lighting system is not required in a Group C <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1271_2.5.0.xml#_f68a626d-6a81-4785-95fa-c032c987c28e" id="_e9cd1311-c78c-41a4-8676-53ebb4391ed0" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">farm building</xref>.</li></ol></subclause></clause>